%% Diagram: IntersectionObserver sentinel — end-to-end event flow
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Scroll as Scroll Container
    participant Sentinel as Bottom Sentinel
    participant IO as IntersectionObserver
    participant App as Feed State (TanStack Query)
    participant API as Backend
    participant List as Virtual List

    Note over IO: rootMargin "0px 0px 200px 0px"<br/>threshold 0
    User->>Scroll: scrolls down
    Scroll-->>Sentinel: enters expanded root box<br/>(viewport + 200px)
    Sentinel-->>IO: layout intersection observed
    IO-->>App: callback (batched, async)<br/>entry.isIntersecting = true
    App->>App: dedupe (in-flight cursor token)
    App->>API: GET /feed?cursor=...<br/>AbortController.signal
    Note over API: keyset query<br/>WHERE (created_at,id) < cursor<br/>LIMIT pageSize
    API-->>App: { items, nextCursor }
    App->>List: append page to cache (maxPages cap)
    List->>Sentinel: re-position below new last item
    List-->>User: paint visible window<br/>(no main-thread scroll block)
    Note over App,List: Next intersection waits until<br/>sentinel re-enters root box.
